title: The UnDailing 11/30: NFL, Ajit Pai, Cyber Monday, Moderna, Monolith, Long Weekend TV Dispatch
itunes:title: The UnDailing 11/30: NFL, Ajit Pai, Cyber Monday, Moderna, Monolith, Long Weekend TV Dispatch
description:
On this edition of The UnDailing Jack and Miles discuss the spread of COVID within the NFL, Ajit Pai will be stepping down next year, today is Cyber Monday and the deals are flying, Moderna appears to be the most trustworthy place for our vaccine hopes, another Monolith has popped up in Romania, and what everyone watched over the long weekend!
